title: House of the Dragon: From Stags to Riches
description:
This week on House of the Dragon, there's a stag hunt, more unsavory betrothal suggestions, and a confrontation with an enemy feared across all of Westeros: tiny crabs!

Watch the recap here:  https://www.patreon.com/posts/71623484?pr=true
